# Vite — copy to ``frontend/.env`` for local dev (or set in CI / host).
# https://vitejs.dev/guide/env-and-mode.html
#
# Forgot / reset email is in-app (``#/forget-pass``) and uses ``POST /api/auth/forgot-password``
# (orchestrator → Auth0 ``/dbconnections/change_password``). Same Auth0 app as login.
